    <title type="html"><![CDATA[[旅遊]中國江西省(Day2)]]></title>
    <link href="http://blog.sammylin.tw/travel-chinas-jiangxi-province-day2/"/>
    <updated>2011-08-31T00:00:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://blog.sammylin.tw/travel-chinas-jiangxi-province-day2</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><p>一早睡醒之後，上午的行程都是在開會，所以沒什麼好介紹的，每次吃飯我都不會帶相機去，所以沒辦法跟各位介紹，我只能說，江西大部份都是吃辣的，會怕辣的人就要考慮一下了，如果沒辦法的話，就帶瓶胃藥吧，因為同行的大哥們很多都拉到屁屁都會辣~</p>  <p><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image12.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image_thumb12.png" width="544" height="234" /></a></p>  <p>今天下午的第一站我們來到了「江西省吉安市橫江鎮公塘村」這邊是被江西省委農工部、省旅遊局等部門被評為「江西省生態新農村」、「江西省鄉村旅遊示範點」，在中國大陸有很多像這樣子的地方，尤其是被共產黨住過的地方更容易被評為什麼示範點的，就是一個「紅色旅遊」要大家必走的地方，像這裡就是曾經被「中國紅軍第五軍第十四師師部舊址」，所以很多建築被保存著大部份都沒人住啦。</p><!--more--><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image13.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image_thumb13.png" width="400" height="419" /></a>    <p><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image14.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image_thumb14.png" width="544" height="407" /></a></p>  <p><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image15.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image_thumb15.png" width="544" height="299" /></a></p>  <p><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image16.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image_thumb16.png" width="544" height="354" /></a></p>  <p><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image17.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image_thumb17.png" width="544" height="392" /></a></p>  <p><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image18.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image_thumb18.png" width="544" height="372" /></a>.</p>  <p><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image19.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image_thumb19.png" width="544" height="405" /></a></p>  <p align="center"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image20.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image_thumb20.png" width="409" height="544" /></a></p>  <p align="center"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image21.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image_thumb21.png" width="405" height="404" /></a></p>  <p align="center"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image22.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image_thumb22.png" width="408" height="535" /></a></p>  <p align="center"><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image23.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image_thumb23.png" width="544" height="399" /></a></p>  <p align="center">很誇張的下起了一場大雨，大家都被淋的差不多了 = =|||</p>  <table border="1" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" width="540"><tbody>     <tr>       <td valign="top" width="540"><span style="font-size: x-small">名稱：公塘村           <br />地點：江西省吉安市橫江鎮</span></td>     </tr>   </tbody></table>  <p align="center"><iframe height="350" marginheight="0" src="http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%B1%9F%E8%A5%BF%E7%9C%81%E5%90%89%E5%AE%89%E5%B8%82%E5%85%AC%E5%A1%98%E6%9D%91&amp;aq=t&amp;sll=29.299579,115.976524&amp;sspn=0.118863,0.154324&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=China+Jiangxi+Yichun+Zhangshu%E5%85%AC%E5%A1%98%E6%9D%91&amp;ll=27.983986,115.309684&amp;spn=0.030091,0.038581&amp;z=14&amp;output=embed" frameborder="0" width="425" marginwidth="0" scrolling="no"></iframe>    <br /><small><a style="text-align: left; color: #0000ff" href="http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%B1%9F%E8%A5%BF%E7%9C%81%E5%90%89%E5%AE%89%E5%B8%82%E5%85%AC%E5%A1%98%E6%9D%91&amp;aq=t&amp;sll=29.299579,115.976524&amp;sspn=0.118863,0.154324&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=China+Jiangxi+Yichun+Zhangshu%E5%85%AC%E5%A1%98%E6%9D%91&amp;ll=27.983986,115.309684&amp;spn=0.030091,0.038581&amp;z=14">View Larger Map</a></small></p>  <p align="center">本來大家想等到雨小一點我們在衝上遊覽車(中國叫大巴)，但雨勢看來沒有變小的樣子，我們只好一把鼻涕一把眼淚的衝上遊覽車上去，之後到了下一個行程「文天祥紀念館」</p>  <p><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image24.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image_thumb24.png" width="544" height="404" /></a></p>  <p><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image25.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image_thumb25.png" width="407" height="411" /></a></p>  <p><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image26.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/image_thumb26.png" width="544" height="403" /></a></p>  <p>其實裡面就是介紹文天祥的事蹟，我對風景比較有興趣，所以導覽在講什麼我就沒去理他了，哈哈~</p>  <table border="1" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" width="540"><tbody>     <tr>       <td valign="top" width="540"><span style="font-size: x-small">名稱：文天祥紀念館           <br />地點：江西省吉安市吉安縣</span></td>     </tr>   </tbody></table>  <p><iframe height="350" marginheight="0" src="http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%B1%9F%E8%A5%BF%E7%9C%81%E5%90%89%E5%AE%89%E5%B8%82%E6%96%87%E5%A4%A9%E7%A5%A5%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E9%A4%A8&amp;aq=1&amp;sll=27.98417,115.309603&amp;sspn=0.013529,0.01929&amp;vpsrc=0&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%B1%9F%E8%A5%BF%E7%9C%81%E5%90%89%E5%AE%89%E5%B8%82%E6%96%87%E5%A4%A9%E7%A5%A5%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E9%A4%A8&amp;ll=27.043676,114.926729&amp;spn=0.019876,0.032015&amp;output=embed" frameborder="0" width="425" marginwidth="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></p></p>

